10/07/2006
DUBROVNIK, Croatia -- An event titled "Croatia Summit 2006" opened in the Adriatic city of Dubrovnik on Monday (10 July), drawing state and government leaders, international representatives and foreign experts. 
The two-day conference will focus on the future of Southeast Europe, Euro-Atlantic integration processes in the region, and European security. 
(Vjesnik, Novi list, HRT - 10/07/06)
